    mpegvideo_enc: enable rtp_mode when multiple slices are used
    
    Currently, multiple slices with just one thread produce corrupted
    output.
    
    Additionally, enable slice structured mode for h263(+)
    
    Bug-Id: 912
    CC: libav-stabl@libav.org

